metadata.name: Cherkas Anna - Swan
metadata.description:
Symbolic revival
December 2021 , Ukraine, Kharkiv.

This self-portrait serves as an interaction between the environment and the perception of
oneself in it.It all starts from the middle.

The author symbolizes himself with a white swan. The goal of the project is openness and
acceptance of your body. Reflection of the symphony, with the help of the body and feminine
natural beauty, in a symbolic image.
According to belief, the bird is equated with human qualities. They are a symbol of true
sincere feelings, pure and mutual love. According to the sign, the swan is a bird of poets. A
meeting with him is considered lucky.

5,94 MB, 4895x3989px , digital picture
Canon 700d
